Take a break from the usual meaty dishes, and recreate this marvelous vegan truffle wild mushroom gnocchi. “Truffle Wild Mushroom Gnocchi is a tasty, melt in your mouth vegan meal, perfect for the whole family or group of friends,” says Wesli Charles Jacobs, Executive Sous Chef at The Table Bay hotel.  Impress your loved ones over an intimate dinner party, and show off your chef skills by recreating this truffle wild mushroom gnocchi, which they will be sure to love. ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Easy lemon butter fish For the gnocchi For the sauce  For the vegetables For plating and serving  This recipe was supplied by Executive Sous Chef at The Table Bay Hotel, Wesli Charles Jacobs